This project is ensure a persistent distributed event consumption and
generation; i.e. there can m-sources of events and n-consumers where m & n are
non-negative.
It is intended to serve a wide are of persistent storage from various NoSQL 
and/or NOSQL, SQL based RDBMS and Object database.
It is also intended to serve a clustered environment using Atmosphere's cluster
support.
Primary and preliminary implementation will be based on Atmosphere (Comet) and
later, besides Pushing, Pulling will also be supported using an Atom feed.

